','password_changed','Password cambiata con successo'),(66,1,'Error Changing Password BG','error_change_password','Грешка при промяна на паролата'),(66,2,'Error Changing Password EN','error_change_password','Error changing password'),(66,3,'Error Changing Password ES','error_change_password','Error modificando la contraseña'),(66,4,'Error Changing Password FR','error_change_password','Oups, une erreur est survenue pendant le changement de mot de passe'),(66,5,'Error Changing Password IT','error_change_password','Errore nel cambiare la password'),(67,1,'Initial Questionnaire Q1 BG','question_text','Доколко си запознат с концепцията за дигитално замърсяване и неговото въздействие върху околната среда? (1. изобщо не, 5. експерт)'),(67,2,'Initial Questionnaire Question 1 EN','question_text','How familiar are you with the concept of digital pollution and its impact on the environment?'),(67,3,'Initial Questionnaire Question 1 ES','question_text','¿Estás familiarizado con el concepto de contaminación digital y su impacto en el medio ambiente?'),(67,4,'Initial Questionnaire Question 1 FR','question_text','Sais-tu ce qu’est la pollution numérique ? (1. Pas du tout ;10. Oui, très bien)'),(67,5,'Initial Questionnaire Question 1 IT','question_text','Quanto conosci il concetto di inquinamento digitale e il suo impatto sull\'ambiente?(1. Per niente; 10. Sì, molto bene)'),(68,1,'Initial Questionnaire Q2 BG','question_text','Доколко си запознат с добри практики, свързани с отговорното използване на технологиите и със зелените технологии(1. изобщо не, 5. експерт)'),(68,2,'Initial Questionnaire Question 2 EN','question_text','How familiar are you with practices related to responsible use of technology and green computing?'),(68,3,'Initial Questionnaire Question 2 ES','question_text','¿Estás familiarizado con las prácticas relacionadas con el uso responsable de la tecnología y la informática ecológica?'),(68,4,'Initial Questionnaire Question 2 FR','question_text','Connais-tu des pratiques d’utilisation responsable du numérique ? (1. Aucune, 10. Oui, beaucoup)'),(68,5,'Initial Questionnaire Question 2 IT','question_text','Hai familiarità con le pratiche relative all\'uso responsabile della tecnologia e del green computing?(1. Per niente; 10. Sì, molto bene)'),(69,1,'Initial Questionnaire Q3 BG','question_text','Доколко смяташ, че е важно хората да предприемат стъпки за намаляване на дигиталното замърсяване и да предприемат действия за преминаването към зелени технологии?  (1. изобщо не е важно, 5. изключително важно)'),(69,2,'Initial Questionnaire Question 3 EN','question_text','How important do you believe it is for individuals to take steps towards reducing digitalpollution and adopting green computing practices?'),(69,3,'Initial Questionnaire Question 3 ES','question_text','¿Hasta qué punto crees que es importante que las personas tomen medidas para reducir la contaminación digital y adoptar prácticas informáticas ecológicas?'),(69,4,'Initial Questionnaire Question 3 FR','question_text','Selon toi, est-il important de réduire la pollution numérique ? (1. Pas important, 10. Très important)'),(69,5,'Initial Questionnaire Question 3 IT','question_text','Quanto è importante per le persone adottare misure per ridurre l\'inquinamento digitale e adottare pratiche di green computing?(1. Per niente; 10. Sì, molto bene)'),(70,1,'Select Difficulty BG',NULL,'Избери нивото на трудност, на което искаш да започнеш. Препоръчваме да започнеш на по-лесна трудност.'),(70,2,'Select Difficulty EN',NULL,'Select which level you want to play. You can start with easy and level up later, or start at a higher level if you feel like it.'),(70,3,'Select Difficulty ES',NULL,'Selecciona el nivel en el que quieres jugar. Puedes empezar con un nivel fácil y subir de nivel más adelante, o empezar en un nivel superior si te apetece'),(70,4,'Select Difficulty FR',NULL,'Sélectionne le niveau auquel tu souhaites jouer. Tu peux commencer par le niveau facile et passer au niveau supérieur plus tard, ou commencer à un niveau plus élevé si tu en as envie.'),(70,5,'Select Difficulty IT',NULL,'Seleziona il livello che vuoi per giocare. Si può iniziare con facile e salire di livello più tardi, o iniziare a un livello superiore, se ne avete voglia.'),(71,1,'Story Introduction Part 1 BG',NULL,'От години човечеството знае, че не може да продължава да живее по този разрушителен начин. \n\nЗнаеш ли, [player name], че дори и най-малките ни действия имат огромно въздействие върху околната среда? \n\nСега си част от екипа на GreenCo. Време е за действие. \n\nЧрез червеева дупка ще пътуваш между настоящето на Земята и бъдещето на Марс, където ще изпълняваш различни мисии. \n\nДекарт, Вера, Керана и Мартон ще ти помагат в различните мисии. \n\nС твоята помощ, [player name], може би ще успеем да спасим човечеството и да пренапишем историята.'),(71,2,'Story Introduction Part 1 EN',NULL,'For years, people knew that it could not continue on this path of destruction. \n\nDid you know, [player name], that small acts have a tremendous environmental impact? \n\nNow, you are part of the GreenCo team. It\'s time to act. \n\nThrough a wormhole, you will travel to the present on Earth and the future on Mars to complete different missions. \n\nDeckard, Vera, Kerana and Marton will guide you on every planet. \n\nWith your help, [player name], we might be able to save humanity and change history.'),(71,3,'Story Introduction Part 1 ES',NULL,'Durante años, la gente supo que no podía continuar por este camino de destrucción. \n\n¿Sabías [player name] que los pequeños actos tienen un tremendo impacto medioambiental? \n\nAhora formas parte del equipo GreenCo. ¡Es hora de actuar! \n\nA través de un agujero de gusano, viajarás al presente en la Tierra y al futuro en Marte para completar diferentes misiones. \n\nDeckart, Vera, Kerana y Marton te guiarán en cada planeta. \n\nCon tu ayuda, [player name], quizá podamos salvar a la humanidad y cambiar la historia.'),(71,4,'Story Introduction Part 1 FR',NULL,'[player name], sais-tu que les petits gestes ont un impact considérable sur l\'environnement ? \n\nMaintenant, tu fais partie de l\'équipe GreenCo. Il est temps d\'agir.\n\nÀ travers un vortex, tu voyageras dans le présent sur Terre et dans le futur sur Mars pour accomplir différentes missions. \n\nDeckard, Vera, Kerana et Marton te guideront sur chaque planète. \n\nAvec ton aide, [player name], nous pourrons peut-être sauver l\'humanité et changer l\'histoire.'),(71,5,'Story Introduction Part 1 IT',NULL,'Per anni, la gente sapeva che non poteva continuare su questa strada di distruzione. Lo sapevi, [player name], che i piccoli artisti hanno un enorme impatto ambientale? Ora, fai parte della squadra GreenCo. È ora di agire. Attraverso un tunnel spaziale, viaggerai verso il presente sulla Terra e il futuro su Marte per completare diverse missioni. Deckart, Vera, Kerana e Marton ti guideranno su ogni pianeta. Con il tuo aiuto, [player name], potremmo essere in grado di salvare l\'umanità e cambiare la storia.'),(72,1,'Story Introduction Part 2 Deckard BG',NULL,'Здравей, [player name]! Благодаря ти за помощта!\n\nТрябва да изпълниш общо осем мисии, за да спасиш човечеството. Мисиите са разпределени на две планети, а именно на Земята и на Марс. На всяка планета има четири различни мисии, в които можеш да се включиш. \n\nМежду другото, аз съм Декарт и ще ти помагам в мисиите, свързани с темата за потребление на енергия. '),(72,2,'Story Introduction Part 2 Deckard EN',NULL,'Hello, [player name]. Thank you very much for your help. \n\nYou must complete eight missions on Earth and Mars to save humanity. On each planet, you will find four different missions. \n\nBy the way, I\'m Deckard, and I will be your guide through the Energy Consumption missions. \n\nVera:'),(72,3,'Story Introduction Part 2 Deckard ES',NULL,'Hola [player name]. Muchas gracias por tu ayuda. \n\nDebes completar un total de ocho misiones entre la Tierra y Marte para salvar a la humanidad. En cada planeta, encontrarás cuatro misiones diferentes. \n\nPor cierto, soy Deckard, y seré tu guía en las misiones de Consumo de Energía.'),(72,4,'Story Introduction Part 2 Deckard FR',NULL,'Bonjour, [player name]. Merci beaucoup pour ton aide. \n\nTu vas devoir accomplir 8 missions sur la Terre et sur Mars pour sauver l\'humanité. Sur chaque planète, on te proposera quatre missions différentes. \n\nAu fait, je m\'appelle Deckard et je serai ton guide pour les missions relatives à la consommation d\'énergie. \n\nEt maintenant, laisse-moi te présenter Vera.'),(72,5,'Story Introduction Part 2 Deckard IT',NULL,'Ciao, [player name]. Grazie mille per il vostro aiuto. Devi completare otto missioni sulla Terra e su Marte per salvare l\'umanità. Su ogni pianeta, troverete quattro diverse missioni. A proposito, sono Deckard, e sarò la vostra guida nelle missioni di consumo energetico. Vera:'),(73,1,'Story Introduction Part 2 Vera BG',NULL,'Здравей, [player name]! Аз съм Вера и съм специалист в рециклирането на електронни отпадъци. \n\nВсяка задача ти носи бронзови, сребърни и златни значки. Когато получиш златна значка, значи си изпълнил мисията успешно.'),(73,2,'Story Introduction Part 2 Vera EN',NULL,'Hi, [player name]. I´m Vera, and I specialise in E-Waste Recycling. \n\nIn each mission, you will receive bronze, silver and gold badges. When you get a golden badge, you have completed the mission.'),(73,3,'Story Introduction Part 2 Vera ES',NULL,'Hola, [player name]. Soy Vera, y estoy especializada en Reciclaje de Residuos Electrónicos. \n\nEn cada misión, recibirás insignias de bronce, plata y oro. Cuando consigas una insignia de oro, habrás completado la misión.'),(73,4,'Story Introduction Part 2 Vera FR',NULL,'Salut [player name]. Je m\'appelle Vera et je suis spécialisée dans le recyclage des déchets électroniques. \n\nPour chaque mission, tu recevras un badge, en bronze, en argent ou en or. Tu termines la mission quand tu obtiens le badge d\'or.'),(73,5,'Story Introduction Part 2 Vera IT',NULL,'Ciao, [nome giocatore]. Sono Vera, e sono specializzata in riciclo di e-rifiuti (rifiuti elettronici) . In ogni missione, riceverai distintivi in bronzo, argento e oro. Quando ottieni un distintivo d\'oro, hai completato la missione.'),(74,2,'Story Introduction Part 3 Kerana EN',NULL,'We are delighted you are with us! I am Kerana, and I will be your guide in the missions of the Earth and Mars Initiatives. [player name], you will earn points for each mission in addition to badges. We have recruited other interns, and the points wil be on a scoreboard.'),(74,3,'Story Introduction Part 3 Kerana ES',NULL,'¡Estamos encantados de que estés con nosotros! Soy Kerana, y seré tu guía en las misiones de las Iniciativas Tierra y Marte. [player name], ganarás puntos por cada misión, además de insignias. Hemos reclutado a otros becarios, y los puntos aparecerán en un marcador.'),(74,4,'Story Introduction Part 3 Kerana FR',NULL,'Je suis Kerana, et je serai ta guide pour les missions relatives aux Initiatives sur Terre et sur Mars. En accomplissant les missions, tu gagneras des points en plus des badges. Tes points seront inscrits sur un tableau d\'affichage.'),(74,5,'Story Introduction Part 3 Kerana IT',NULL,'Siamo lieti che tu sia con noi! Io sono Kerana, e sarò la tua guida nelle missioni inziative sulla Terra e su Marte . [player name], guadagnerai punti per ogni missione oltre ai badge. Abbiamo reclutato altri tirocinanti, e i punti saranno su un tabellone.'),(75,1,'Story Introduction Part 3 Marton BG',NULL,'Ще трябва да дадеш всичко от себе си, за да спасиш човечеството. Аз съм Мартон, и съм специалист в областта законодателството. Не забравяй, че на всяка планета трябва да изпълниш четири мисии. Готов ли си? Да вървим!'),(75,2,'Story Introduction Part 3 Marton EN',NULL,'So, try your best to save humanity together, and you can be the best. I´m Marton, specialising in Legislation. Remember that four missions have to be completed on each planet. Are you ready? Let\'s go to the spaceship!'),(75,3,'Story Introduction Part 3 Marton ES',NULL,'Así que, esfuérzate al máximo para salvar juntos a la humanidad, y podrás ser el mejor. Soy Marton, especializado en Legislación. Recuerda que hay que completar cuatro misiones en cada planeta. ¿Estás preparado? ¡Vamos a la nave espacial!'),(75,4,'Story Introduction Part 3 Marton FR',NULL,'Je suis Marton, spécialisé dans la législation. N\'oublie pas que 4 missions doivent être accomplies sur chaque planète. Tu es prêt(e ? Alors commençons !'),(75,5,'Story Introduction Part 3 Marton IT',NULL,'Quindi, fai del tuo meglio per salvare l\'umanità insieme, e puoi essere il migliore. Sono Marton, specializzata in legislazione. Ricordate che quattro missioni devono essere completate su ogni pianeta. Allora, sei pronto, eh? Andiamo alla nave spaziale!'),(76,1,'Decide your adventure BG',NULL,'Време е, [player name], да вземеш първото си решение. Къде предпочиташ да започнеш - на Земята, или на Марс в бъдещето?'),(76,2,'Decide your adventure EN',NULL,'It\'s time, [player name], to make your first decision. Would you rather start saving the Earth today or prefer to travel to the future and go to Mars?'),(76,3,'Decide your adventure ES',NULL,'Ha llegado el momento de tomar tu primera decisión [player name]. ¿Prefieres comenzar salvando la Tierra o prefieres viajar al futuro e ir a Marte?'),(76,4,'Decide your adventure FR',NULL,'[player name], préfères-tu commencer par sauver la Terre aujourd\'hui, ou voyager dans le futur et aller sur Mars ?'),(76,5,'Decide your adventure IT',NULL,'È il momento, [player name], di prendere la prima decisione. Preferisci iniziare a salvare la Terra oggi o preferisci viaggiare nel futuro e andare su Marte?'),(77,1,'Earth Introduction BG',NULL,'Добре дошъл на Земята, [player name]!\n\nСлед няколко години околната среда ще бъде по-замърсена от ИТ индустрията, отколкото от автомобилите или мотоциклетите, което ще допринесе значително за повишаването на емисиите на парникови газове.\n\nСитуацията е критична и за да можем да продължим да живеем на Земята, трябва да променим навиците си.\n\nТрябва да изпълниш четири мисии. \n\nДекарт, Вера, Керана и Мартон ще ти помагат. Готов ли си?'),(77,2,'Earth Introduction EN',NULL,'Welcome to the Earth, [player name]!!! \n\nIn a few years, the Environment will be more polluted by the Information Technology Industry than by cars or motorcycles, contributing significantly to greenhouse gas emissions. \n\nWe are in a critical situation and must change our habits to continue living on Earth. \n\nYou have four missions to complete. \n\nDeckart, Vera, Kerana and Marton will help you. Are you ready?'),(77,3,'Earth Introduction ES',NULL,'¡¡¡Bienvenido a la Tierra [player name]!!! \n\nDentro de unos años, el Medio Ambiente estará más contaminado por la Industria de la Tecnología de la Información que por los coches o las motos, contribuyendo significativamente a las emisiones de gases de efecto invernadero. \n\nEstamos en una situación crítica y debemos cambiar nuestros hábitos para seguir viviendo en la Tierra. \n\nTienes cuatro misiones que completar. \n\nDeckart, Vera, Kerana y Marton te ayudarán. ¿Estáis preparados?'),(77,4,'Earth Introduction FR',NULL,'Bienvenue sur Terre, [player name] !!! \n\nDans quelques années, l\'environnement sera plus pollué par l\'industrie des technologies de l\'information que par les voitures ou les motos, ce qui contribura de manière significative aux émissions de gaz à effet de serre. \n\nNous sommes dans une situation critique et devons changer nos habitudes pour continuer à vivre sur Terre. \n\nTu as quatre missions à accomplir. \n\nDeckard, Vera, Kerana et Marton t\'aideront. Es-tu prêt(e) ?'),(77,5,'Earth Introduction IT',NULL,'Benvenuti sulla Terra, [player name]!!! Tra qualche anno, l\'ambiente sarà più inquinato dall\'industria delle tecnologie dell\'informazione che dalle automobili o dai motocicli, contribuendo in modo significativo alle emissioni di gas serra. Siamo in una situazione critica e dobbiamo cambiare le nostre abitudini per continuare a vivere sulla Terra. Hai quattro missioni da completare. Deckart, Vera, Kerana e Marton vi aiuteranno. Allora, sei pronto, eh?'),(124,1,'Difficulty level easy BG','difficulty_name','Лесно'),(124,2,'Difficulty level easy EN','difficulty_name','Easy'),(124,3,'Difficulty level easy ES','difficulty_name','Fácil'),(124,4,'Difficulty level easy FR','difficulty_name','Facile'),(124,5,'Difficulty level easy IT','difficulty_name','Facile'),(125,1,'Difficulty level medium english BG','difficulty_name','Средно'),(125,2,'Difficulty level medium english EN','difficulty_name','Medium'),(125,3,'Difficulty level medium english ES','difficulty_name','Medio'),(125,4,'Difficulty level medium english FR','difficulty_name','Moyen'),(125,5,'Difficulty level medium english IT','difficulty_name','Medio'),(126,1,'Difficulty level hard english BG','difficulty_name','Трудно'),(126,2,'Difficulty level hard english EN','difficulty_name','Hard'),(126,3,'Difficulty level hard english ES','difficulty_name','Dificil'),(126,4,'Difficulty level hard english FR','difficulty_name','Difficile'),(126,5,'Difficulty level hard english IT','difficulty_name','Duro'),(127,1,'Planet earth english BG','planet_name','Земя'),(127,2,'Planet earth english EN','planet_name','Earth'),(127,3,'Planet earth english ES','planet_name','Tierra'),(127,4,'Planet earth english FR','planet_name','Terre'),(127,5,'Planet earth english IT','planet_name','Terra'),(128,1,'Planet mars english BG','planet_name','Марс'),(128,2,'Planet mars english EN','planet_name','Mars'),(128,3,'Planet mars english ES','planet_name','Marte'),(128,4,'Planet mars english FR','planet_name','Mars'),(128,5,'Planet mars english IT','planet_name','Marte'),(129,1,'Energy Consumption room BG','level_name','Потребление на енергия'),(129,2,'Energy Consumption room EN','level_name','Energy Consumption'),(129,3,'Energy Consumption room ES','level_name','