ext Question Q1.1 FR','question_text','Comme tu le sais, il est important de réduire la consommation d\'électricité induite par la technologie numérique. Si Internet était un pays, quel aurait été son rang en matière de consommation d\'électricité en 2021 ?'),(500,5,'Text Question Q1.1 IT','question_text','Come sai, è importante ridurre il consumo di energia elettrica indotto dalla tecnologia digitale. Per esempio, Se internet era un paese, sai quale sarebbe stato il suo rango per l\'utilizzo di energia elettrica nel 2021? '),(501,1,'Text Question Q1.2 BG','question_text','Именно поради тази причина е толкова важно да се ограничим в потреблението си на електроенергия, когато това е възможно. Повечето електроуреди консумират енергия дори и в режим на готовност! Знаеш ли как наричаме енергията, която един електроуред консумира в режим на готовност? '),(501,2,'Text Question Q1.2 EN','question_text','It is thus essential to reduce energy consumption whenever it is possible. Most electronic devices consume power in standby mode. Do you know how we call the power an appliance consumes in standby mode?'),(501,3,'Text Question Q1.2 ES','question_text','Por eso es esencial reducir el consumo de energía siempre que sea posible. La mayoría de los aparatos electrónicos consumen energía en modo de espera. ¿Sabes cómo llamamos a la energía que consume un aparato en modo de espera?'),(501,4,'Text Question Q1.2 FR','question_text','Il est donc essentiel de réduire la consommation d’énergie chaque fois que cela est possible. La plupart des appareils électroniques consomment de l\'énergie en mode veille. C\'est vraiment du ...'),(501,5,'Text Question Q1.2 IT','question_text','Per questo motivo è fondamentale ridurre il consumo di energia ogni volta che è possibile. La maggior parte dei dispositivi elettronici consuma energia in modalità standby. Sapete come si chiama l\'energia consumata da un dispositivo in modalità standby?'),(502,1,'Text Question Q1.3c BG','question_text','Ако искаш да намалиш фантомната консумация на електроенергия в дома си, кои уреди от изброените си струва да изключиш или извадиш от електрическата мрежа, когато не ги използваш? '),(502,2,'Text Question Q1.3c EN','question_text','If you want to reduce the vampire power at your home, which appliances among the following are worth switching off or unplugging when you are not using it?'),(502,3,'Text Question Q1.3c ES','question_text','Si quieres reducir la energía vampírica de tu casa, ¿qué electrodomésticos de los siguientes merece la pena apagar o desenchufar cuando no los estés utilizando?'),(502,4,'Text Question Q1.3c FR','question_text','Si tu souhaites réduire ce gaspillage à la maison, quels appareils parmi les suivants peuvent être éteints ou débranchés lorsque tu ne les utilises pas ?'),(502,5,'Text Question Q1.3c IT','question_text','Se vuoi ridurre il vampire power a casa tua, quali elettrodomestici tra i seguenti vale la pena spegnere o scollegare quando non lo stai usando? '),(503,1,'Text Question Q1.4 BG','question_text','Борбата с фантомната консумация на електроенергия не е единственият начин, по който можеш да намалиш потреблението си на електроенергия. Нека разгледаме видео стрийминга, например. Знаеш ли какъв процент е той от общия интернет трафик през 2019 г.? '),(503,2,'Text Question Q1.4 EN','question_text','Fighting against vampire power is not the only way to reduce energy consumption. Let us consider video streaming for example. Do you know what percentage of Internet traffic streaming represented in 2019?'),(503,3,'Text Question Q1.4 ES','question_text','Luchar contra la energía vampírica no es la única forma de reducir el consumo energético. Pensemos, por ejemplo, en el streaming de vídeo. ¿Sabes qué porcentaje del tráfico de Internet representó el streaming en 2019?'),(503,4,'Text Question Q1.4 FR','question_text','Lutter contre le gaspillage n’est pas le seul moyen de réduire sa consommation d’énergie. Prenons par exemple le streaming vidéo. Sais-tu quel pourcentage du trafic Internet cela représentait en 2019 ?'),(503,5,'Text Question Q1.4 IT','question_text','Combattere il vampire power (o energia di standby) non è l\'unico modo per ridurre il consumo energetico. Consideriamo lo streaming video per esempio. Sai quale percentuale di streaming del traffico Internet ha rappresentato nel 2019? '),(504,1,'Text Question Q1.5 BG','question_text','За да можем да стриймваме видео, са необходими много компютри по целия свят. Не можеш да намалиш енергията, която тези компютри консумират, но можеш да избереш устройство, на което да стриймваш видео, което не консумира твърде много енергия. Помогни ми да подредя следните уреди от най-малко към най-много консумиращи енергия (при равни други условия). '),(504,2,'Text Question Q1.5 EN','question_text','To make streaming possible, it requires many computers all over the world. You can not decrease their power consumption, but you can choose an appliance to watch your videos that do not consume too much. Help me to order the following appliances from least to most power consuming (all else being equal).'),(504,3,'Text Question Q1.5 ES','question_text','Para hacer posible el streaming, se necesitan muchos ordenadores en todo el mundo. No puedes disminuir su consumo, pero puedes elegir un aparato para ver tus vídeos que no consuma demasiada energía.\nAyúdame a ordenar los siguientes aparatos de menor a mayor consumo de energía (en igualdad de condiciones).'),(504,4,'Text Question Q1.5 FR','question_text','Pour rendre le streaming possible, il faut de nombreux ordinateurs partout dans le monde. Tu ne peux pas diminuer leur consommation électrique, mais tu peux choisir un appareil pour regarder tes vidéos qui ne consomme pas trop. Aide-moi à classer les appareils suivants du moins au plus consommateur d\'énergie (toutes choses étant égales par ailleurs).'),(504,5,'Text Question Q1.5 IT','question_text','Per rendere possibile lo streaming, richiede molti computer in tutto il mondo. Non è possibile ridurre il loro consumo energetico, ma è possibile scegliere un apparecchio per guardare i video che non consumano troppo. Aiutami a ordinare i seguenti apparecchi dal minimo al più consumo di energia (tutto il resto è uguale). '),(505,1,'Text Question Q1.6 BG','question_text','Ако приемем, че ще избереш да стриймваш видео на смартфона си, вярно ли е, че Wi-Fi връзката ще изисква по-малко електроенергия от 4G връзката? '),(505,2,'Text Question Q1.6 EN','question_text','So you choose to watch streaming on your smartphone. Is it true that a Wi-Fi connection will require less energy than a 4G one?'),(505,3,'Text Question Q1.6 ES','question_text','Así que eliges ver streaming en tu smartphone. ¿Es cierto que una conexión Wi-Fi requiere menos energía que una 4G?'),(505,4,'Text Question Q1.6 FR','question_text','Tu choisis donc de regarder du streaming sur ton smartphone. Est-il vrai qu’une connexion Wi-Fi nécessitera moins d’énergie qu’une connexion 4G ?'),(505,5,'Text Question Q1.6 IT','question_text','Quindi scegli di guardare lo streaming sul tuo smartphone. È vero che una connessione Wi-Fi richiede meno energia di una connessione 4G? '),(506,1,'Text Question Q1.7 BG','question_text','Малките икономии на енергия могат да изглеждат безполезни и нищожни на фона на всичко останало. Затова нека направим някои изчисления. Представи си, че една гейминг конзола консумира 5 вата, докато е в режим на готовност. Да кажем, че за една година тя остава в режим на готовност 20 часа/ден и в продължение на 350 дни. Колко електроенергия ще спестиш, ако вместо това я изключиш от електрическата мрежа? '),(506,2,'Text Question Q1.7 EN','question_text','Small energy savings might look futile to you. So, let’s do some estimation. Imagine that a game station consumes 5 Watts while in standby mode. Consider now that in one year, it stays in standby mode for 20 hours/day, and for 350 days. How much power would he save if he unplugged it instead?'),(506,3,'Text Question Q1.7 ES','question_text','Un pequeño ahorro de energía puede parecerte inútil. Hagamos una estimación. Imaginemos que una consola consume 5 vatios en modo de espera. Considera ahora que, en un año, permanece en modo de espera 20 horas al día, y durante 350 días. ¿Cuánta energía ahorraría si decides desenchufarla?'),(506,4,'Text Question Q1.7 FR','question_text','De petites économies d’énergie peuvent sembler futiles. Alors, faisons une estimation. Imaginons qu\'une station de jeu consomme 5 watts en mode veille. Considérons maintenant qu\'en un an, cette console reste en mode veille 20 heures par jour, et ce pendant 350 jours. Quelle quantité d’énergie économiserait-on si on débranchait la console plutôt que de la laisser en veille?'),(506,5,'Text Question Q1.7 IT','question_text','Un piccolo risparmio energetico potrebbe sembrarti inutile. Quindi, facciamo una stima. Immaginate che una stazione di gioco consumi 5 Watt in modalità standby. Considera ora che in un anno, rimane in modalità standby per 20 ore/ giorno e per 350 giorni. Quanta energia salverebbe se la staccasse invece? '),(507,1,'Text Question Q1.8 BG','question_text','Имаш ли представа какво можеш да захраниш с 35 kWh? '),(507,2,'Text Question Q1.8 EN','question_text','Do you have any idea of what can be powered with 35 kWh?'),(507,3,'Text Question Q1.8 ES','question_text','¿Sabes la cantidad de cosas que se puede alimentar con 35 kWh?'),(507,4,'Text Question Q1.8 FR','question_text','Que peut-on faire avec 35 kWh ?'),(507,5,'Text Question Q1.8 IT','question_text','Avete idea di cosa possa essere alimentato con 35 kWh? '),(508,1,'Text Question Q1.9 BG','question_text','Вярно ли е, че през 2022 г. в света са продадени повече от 5 милиона гейминг конзоли? '),(508,2,'Text Question Q1.9 EN','question_text','Is it true that in 2022, more than 5 million game stations were sold globally?'),(508,3,'Text Question Q1.9 ES','question_text','¿Es cierto que en 2022 se vendieron más de 5 millones de videoconsolas en todo el mundo?'),(508,4,'Text Question Q1.9 FR','question_text','Est-il vrai qu’en 2022, plus de 5 millions de stations de jeux ont été vendues dans le monde ?'),(508,5,'Text Question Q1.9 IT','question_text','È vero che nel 2022 più di 5 milioni di stazioni di gioco sono state vendute a livello globale? '),(509,1,'Text Question Q1.10 BG','question_text','Ако собствениците на 5 милиона гейминг конзоли пестят по 35 kWh годишно, каква ще бъде общата икономия на енергия във ват-часове? '),(509,2,'Text Question Q1.10 EN','question_text','If 5 million gaming station owners achieve savings of 35 kWh per year, what would be the total energy savings in terms of watt-hours?'),(509,3,'Text Question Q1.10 ES','question_text','Si 5 millones de propietarios de videoconsolas consiguen un ahorro de 35 kWh al año, ¿cuál sería el ahorro total de energía en términos de vatios-hora?'),(509,4,'Text Question Q1.10 FR','question_text','Si 5 millions de propriétaires de stations de jeux réalisent 35 kWh d\'économie par an, quelle serait l’économie d’énergie totale en termes de wattheures ?'),(509,5,'Text Question Q1.10 IT','question_text','Se 5 milioni di possessori di stazioni di gioco ottengono un risparmio di 35 kWh all\'anno, quale sarebbe il risparmio energetico totale in termini di wattora? '),(520,1,'Text Question Q2.1 BG','question_text','Мисля, че трябва да започнем от самото начало. Можеш ли да ни помогнеш да определим какво представляват електронните отпадъци? '),(520,2,'Text Question Q2.1 EN','question_text','I think we should start at the very beginning. Could you help us define what e-waste is?'),(520,3,'Text Question Q2.1 ES','question_text','Creo que deberíamos empezar por el principio. ¿Podrías ayudarnos a definir qué es la basura electrónica?'),(520,4,'Text Question Q2.1 FR','question_text','Commençons par le commencement. Peux-tu nous aider à définir ce qu’est un déchet électronique ?'),(520,5,'Text Question Q2.1 IT','question_text','Credo che dovremmo cominciare proprio dall\'inizio. Puoi aiutarci a definire cosa sono i rifiuti elettronici? '),(521,1,'Text Question Q2.2 BG','question_text','Много е важно всички да разберем защо електронните отпадъци се превръщат в такъв проблем. Вярно ли е, че намаляването на количеството на редките и ценни материали е сред основните проблеми, свързани с неправилното изхвърляне на електронни отпадъци? '),(521,2,'Text Question Q2.2 EN','question_text','It is very important that we all understand why electronic waste is becoming such a problem. Is it true that the decrease in rare and valuable materials is among the main concerns, related to the improper disposal of electronic waste?'),(521,3,'Text Question Q2.2 ES','question_text','Es muy importante que todos entendamos por qué los residuos electrónicos se están convirtiendo en un problema. ¿Es cierto que la disminución de materiales raros y valiosos se encuentra entre las principales preocupaciones, relacionadas con la eliminación inadecuada de residuos electrónicos?'),(521,4,'Text Question Q2.2 FR','question_text','Las déchets électroniques deviennent un problème. Est-il vrai que la diminution des matériaux rares et précieux fait partie des principales préoccupations liées à l\'élimination inappropriée des déchets électroniques ?'),(521,5,'Text Question Q2.2 IT','question_text','È molto importante che tutti comprendiamo perché i rifiuti elettronici stanno diventando un problema. È vero che la diminuzione dei materiali rari e pregiati è tra le principali preoccupazioni, legate allo smaltimento improprio dei rifiuti elettronici? '),(522,1,'Text Question Q2.3 BG','question_text','Съществуват някои противоречиви представи за големите домакински уреди. Кои от изброените НЕ се считат за големи домакински уреди? '),(522,2,'Text Question Q2.3 EN','question_text','There has been some misconception about large household appliances. Which of the following are NOT considered large household appliances?'),(522,3,'Text Question Q2.3 ES','question_text','Existe una idea equivocada sobre los grandes electrodomésticos. ¿Cuáles de los siguientes NO se consideran grandes electrodomésticos?'),(522,4,'Text Question Q2.3 FR','question_text','Il existe certaines fausses idées concernant les déchets. Parmi les appareils suivants, lesquels ne sont PAS considérés comme de gros appareils électroménagers ?'),(522,5,'Text Question Q2.3 IT','question_text','C\'è stato qualche equivoco sui grandi elettrodomestici. Quali di questi NON sono considerati grandi elettrodomestici? '),(523,1,'Text Question Q2.4 BG','question_text','Интересно е, че класификацията на електронните отпадъци е трудна за разбиране от толкова много хора! Особена трудност представлява класификацията на лаптопите. Знаеш ли в коя категория уреди попадат лаптопите? '),(523,2,'Text Question Q2.4 EN','question_text','It is interesting that the classification of electronic waste is difficult for so many people to grasp! One particular difficulty is the classification of laptops. Do you know what category of appliances do laptops fall into?'),(523,3,'Text Question Q2.4 ES','question_text','Es interesante que la clasificación de los residuos electrónicos resulte difícil de entender para tanta gente. Una dificultad particular es la clasificación de los ordenadores portátiles. ¿Sabes a qué categoría de aparatos pertenecen los ordenadores portátiles?'),(523,4,'Text Question Q2.4 FR','question_text','La classification des déchets électroniques est parfois difficile à comprendre ! Sais-tu à quelle catégorie d’appareils appartiennent les ordinateurs portables ?'),(523,5,'Text Question Q2.4 IT','question_text','È interessante notare che la classificazione dei rifiuti elettronici è difficile da capire per così tante persone! Una difficoltà particolare è la classificazione dei computer portatili. Sai in quale categoria di elettrodomestici rientrano i laptop? '),(524,1,'Text Question Q2.5 BG','question_text','Повечето от нас не знаят, че по-старите монитори са много трудни за рециклиране поради големите количества олово в тях. Знаеш ли кой е компонентът, който съдържа най-много олово? '),(524,2,'Text Question Q2.5 EN','question_text','Most of us are not aware that older monitors are very hard to recycle because of the large quantities of lead inside. Do you know what the component that contains the most lead is?'),(524,3,'Text Question Q2.5 ES','question_text','La mayoría de nosotros no sabemos que los monitores antiguos son muy difíciles de reciclar debido a las grandes cantidades de plomo que contienen. ¿Sabes cuál es el componente que contiene más plomo?'),(524,4,'Text Question Q2.5 FR','question_text','Les anciens écrans (d’ordinateur ou de télévision) sont très difficiles à recycler en raison de la grande quantité de plomb qu’ils contiennent. Sais-tu quel est le composant qui contient le plus de plomb dans les anciens écrans ?'),(524,5,'Text Question Q2.5 IT','question_text','La maggior parte di noi non sono consapevoli che i monitor più vecchi sono molto difficili da riciclare a causa delle grandi quantità di piombo all\'interno. Sai qual è il componente che contiene più piombo? '),(525,1,'Text Question Q2.6 BG','question_text','Можем ли да поговорим повече за големите домакински уреди? Вярно ли е, че за да бъдат рециклирани, те трябва да бъдат взети от специализирани фирми, които безопасно ги разглобяват за рециклиране и повторна употреба? '),(525,2,'Text Question Q2.6 EN','question_text','Can we talk more about large household appliances? Is it true that to recycle them, they can be picked up by dedicated companies that safely dismantle them for recycling and reuse?'),(525,3,'Text Question Q2.6 ES','question_text','¿Podemos hablar más sobre los grandes electrodomésticos? ¿Es cierto que, para reciclarlos, pueden recogerlos empresas especializadas que los desmontan de forma segura para reciclarlos y reutilizarlos?'),(525,4,'Text Question Q2.6 FR','question_text','Parlons maintenant des gros électroménagers. Est-il vrai que pour les recycler, ils peuvent être récupérés par des entreprises dédiées qui les démantèlent en toute sécurité pour les recycler et les réutiliser ?'),(525,5,'Text Question Q2.6 IT','question_text','Possiamo parlare di più di grandi elettrodomestici? È vero che per riciclarli possono essere raccolti da aziende dedicate che li smantellano in modo sicuro per il riciclaggio e il riutilizzo? '),(526,1,'Text Question Q2.7 BG','question_text','Малко хора знаят кои са най-често срещаните опасни вещества в електронните отпадъци. Можеш ли да изброиш някои от тях? '),(526,2,'Text Question Q2.7 EN','question_text','Not many people know the most mentioned hazardous substances in electronic waste. Can you list a few?'),(526,3,'Text Question Q2.7 ES','question_text','No mucha gente conoce las sustancias peligrosas más mencionadas en los residuos electrónicos. ¿Puede enumerar algunas?'),(526,4,'Text Question Q2.7 FR','question_text','Peu de gens connaissent les substances dangereuses les plus mentionnées dans les déchets électroniques. Peux-tu en énumérer quelques-unes ?'),(526,5,'Text Question Q2.7 IT','question_text','Non molte persone conoscono le sostanze pericolose più menzionate nei rifiuti elettronici. Puoi elencarne alcuni? '),(527,1,'Text Question Q2.8 BG','question_text','Съществува известно объркване относно съкращението ОЕЕО. Какво означава то? '),(527,2,'Text Question Q2.8 EN','question_text','There has been some confusion about the abbreviation WEEE. What does it stand for?'),(527,3,'Text Question Q2.8 ES','question_text','Ha habido cierta confusión sobre la abreviatura RAEE. ¿Qué significa? '),(527,4,'Text Question Q2.8 FR','question_text','Sais-tu ce que signifie l\'abréviation DEEE ?'),(527,5,'Text Question Q2.8 IT','question_text','C\'è stata una certa confusione sull\'abbreviazione RAEE. Che cosa sta per? '),(528,1,'Text Question Q2.9 BG','question_text','Много хора не разбират, че изхвърлянето на стария лаптоп се различава от изхвърлянето на други електроуреди, тъй като преди да го рециклираш, трябва да унищожиш данните на него. Можеш ли да обобщиш защо това е важно? '),(528,2,'Text Question Q2.9 EN','question_text','Most people do not understand that disposing of your old laptop is different from other technology, as you must destroy the data before you recycle it. Can you summarise why this is important?'),(528,3,'Text Question Q2.9 ES','question_text','La mayoría de la gente no entiende que deshacerse de su viejo portátil es diferente de otras tecnologías, ya que hay que destruir los datos antes de reciclarlo. ¿Puedes indicar por qué es importante? '),(528,4,'Text Question Q2.9 FR','question_text','Pourquoi est-il si important de détruire les données de ton ancien ordinateur portable avant de le mettre au rebut ?'),(528,5,'Text Question Q2.9 IT','question_text','La maggior parte delle persone non capisce che lo smaltimento del vostro vecchio computer portatile è diverso da altre tecnologie, in quanto è necessario distruggere i dati prima di riciclarlo. Può riassumere perché questo è importante? '),(529,1,'Text Question Q2.10 BG','question_text','Можеш ли да ни кажеш дали е вярно, че батериите не са категория електронни отпадъци? '),(529,2,'Text Question Q2.10 EN','question_text','Can you tell us if it is true that batteries are not a category of electronic waste?'),(529,3,'Text Question Q2.10 ES','question_text','¿Puede decirnos si es cierto que las pilas no son una categoría de residuos electrónicos?'),(529,4,'Text Question Q2.10 FR','question_text','Est-il vrai que les piles n\'appartiennent pas à la catégorie de déchets électroniques ?'),(529,5,'Text Question Q2.10 IT','question_text','Può dirci se è vero che le batterie non sono una categoria di rifiuti elettronici? '),(530,1,'Text Question Q3.1 BG','question_text','На 25 септември 2015 г. държавите членки на ______ ратифицират Програмата до ______ г. за устойчиво развитие.'),(530,2,'Text Question Q3.1 EN','question_text','On September 25, 2015, all United ______ member states ratified the ______Agenda for Sustainable Development.'),(530,3,'Text Question Q3.1 ES','question_text','El 25 de septiembre de 2015, todos los miembros de las ______ Unidas ratificaron la Agenda ______ para el Desarrollo Sostenible'),(530,4,'Text Question Q3.1 FR','question_text','Le 25 septembre 2015, tous les États membres des ______ Unies ont ratifié l’Agenda ______ pour le développement durable.'),(530,5,'Text Question Q3.1 IT','question_text','Il 25 settembre 2015 tutti gli ______ membri hanno ratificato l\'Agenda________  per lo Sviluppo Sostenibile. '),(531,1,'Text Question Q3.2 BG','question_text','В кой европейски град е прието международно споразумение за изменението на климата? '),(531,2,'Text Question Q3.2 EN','question_text','In which European city was adopted an international climate change agreement?'),(531,3,'Text Question Q3.2 ES','question_text','¿En qué ciudad europea se adoptó un acuerdo internacional sobre el cambio climático?'),(531,4,'Text Question Q3.2 FR','question_text','Dans quelle ville européenne a été adopté un accord international sur le changement climatique ?'),(531,5,'Text Question Q3.2 IT','question_text','In quale città europea è stato adottato un accordo internazionale sul cambiamento climatico? '),(532,1,'Text Question Q3.3 BG','question_text','Климатична неутралност касае възстановяване на баланса по отношение на вредните емисии до състоянието отпреди сто и половина века. Вярно ли е това твърдение? '),(532,2,'Text Question Q3.3 EN','question_text','Climate neutrality means restoring the planet\'s balance, in terms of emissions and removals, to the pre-industrial levels (around 1850). True or false?'),(532,3,'Text Question Q3.3 ES','question_text','La neutralidad climática significa restablecer el equilibrio del planeta, en términos de emisiones y absorciones a la era preindustrial(1850)  ¿Es verdadero o falso?'),(532,4,'Text Question Q3.3 FR','question_text','Vrai ou Faux ? La neutralité climatique signifie rétablir l\'équilibre des émissions et des absorptions des gaz à effets de serre, pour retrouver l\'état d\'avant l\'aire industrielle.'),(532,5,'Text Question Q3.3 IT','question_text','Neutralità climatica significa riportare l\'equilibrio del pianeta, in termini di emissioni e rimozioni, allo stato in cui era cento secoli e mezzo fa. È vero o falso? '),(533,1,'Text Question Q3.4 BG','question_text','Колко цели за устойчиво развитие има Програмата на ООН до 2030 г.? '),(533,2,'Text Question Q3.4 EN','question_text','How many sustainable development goals has the United Nations 2030 Agenda?'),(533,3,'Text Question Q3.4 ES','question_text','¿Cuántos objetivos de desarrollo sostenible tiene la Agenda 2030 de las Naciones Unidas?'),(533,4,'Text Question Q3.4 FR','question_text','Combien d’objectifs de développement durable compte l’Agenda 2030 des Nations Unies ?'),(533,5,'Text Question Q3.4 IT','question_text','Quanti obiettivi di sviluppo sostenibile ha l\'Agenda 2030 delle Nazioni Unite? '),(534,1,'Text Question Q3.5 BG','question_text','Парижкото споразумение има за цел да: '),(534,2,'Text Question Q3.5 EN','question_text','The Paris agreement aimed to:'),(534,3,'Text Question Q3.5 ES','question_text','El acuerdo de París pretendía:'),(534,4,'Text Question Q3.5 FR','question_text','L’accord de Paris vise à :'),(534,5,'Text Question Q3.5 IT','question_text','l\'accordo di Parigi mirava a: '),(535,1,'Text Question Q3.6 BG','question_text','Тринадесетата цел на Програмата на ООН до 2030 г. се фокусира върху необходимостта от предприемане на спешни действия за борба с изменението на климата и неговите последици, които засягат всички страни по света. Какво е общото определение на тази цел?'),(535,2,'Text Question Q3.6 EN','question_text','The 13th Goal of the Agenda 2030 focuses on the need to take urgent action to end climate change, which affects every country in the world. What is the definition of this goal?'),(535,3,'Text Question Q3.6 ES','question_text','El Objetivo 13 de la Agenda 2030 se centra en la necesidad de tomar medidas urgentes para acabar con el cambio climático, que afecta a todos los países del mundo. ¿Cuál es la definición de este objetivo?'),(535,4,'Text Question Q3.6 FR','question_text','L\'objectif 13 de l’Agenda 2030 insiste sur la nécessité de prendre des mesures urgentes pour mettre fin au réchauffement planétaire, qui affecte tous les pays du monde. Quel est cet objectif ?'),(535,5,'Text Question Q3.6 IT','question_text','Il 13° Obiettivo dell\'Agenda 2030 si concentra sulla necessità di intraprendere azioni urgenti per porre fine al cambiamento climatico, che interessa tutti i Paesi del mondo. Qual è la definizione di questo obiettivo?'),(536,1,'Text Question Q3.7 BG','question_text','ЕС се съгласи да намали емисиите с поне ______ % до 2030 г., в сравнение с ангажимента си за ______ % през 2014 г. '),(536,2,'Text Question Q3.7 EN','question_text','The EU has agreed to cut emissions by at least ______ % by 2030, up from its ______ % commitment in 2014.'),(536,3,'Text Question Q3.7 ES','question_text','La UE ha acordado reducir las emisiones al menos un ______% para 2030, lo que supone un aumento respecto a su compromiso del 2014 de un ______%'),(536,4,'Text Question Q3.7 FR','question_text','L’UE s’est engagée à réduire ses émissions d’au moins ______ % d’ici 2030, alors qu\'il était de ______ % en 2014.'),(536,5,'Text Question Q3.7 IT','question_text','l\'UE ha accettato di ridurre le emissioni di almeno il ______ % entro il 2030, rispetto al suo impegno del ______ % nel 2014. '),(537,1,'Text Question Q3.8 BG','question_text','Програмата до 2030 г. има 90 интегрирани и неделими цели, обхващащи икономическата, социалната и екологичната сфера. Вярно или невярно е това? '),(537,2,'Text Question Q3.8 EN','question_text','The 2030 Agenda has 90 integrated and indivisible targets spanning the economic, social and environmental spheres. It´s true or false?'),(537,3,'Text Question Q3.8 ES','question_text','La Agenda 2030 tiene 90 obj