 2030 aims at building resilient infrastructure, promoting inclusive and sustainable industrialization. What is the definition of this goal?'),(539,3,'Text Question Q3.10 ES','question_text','El 9º Objetivo de la Agenda 2030 pretende construir infraestructuras resilientes y promover una industrialización inclusiva y sostenible. ¿Cuál es la definición de este objetivo?'),(539,4,'Text Question Q3.10 FR','question_text','L\'objectif 9 de l’Agenda 2030 vise à encourager un développement économique durable. Quel est cet objectif ?'),(539,5,'Text Question Q3.10 IT','question_text','Il 9° Obiettivo dell\'Agenda 2030 mira a costruire infrastrutture resilienti e a promuovere un\'industrializzazione inclusiva e sostenibile. Qual è la definizione di questo obiettivo?'),(540,1,'Text Question Q4.1 BG','question_text','Устойчиво е това развитие, което задоволява настоящите ни нужди, без да застрашава способността на ______ поколения да задоволяват своите. '),(540,2,'Text Question Q4.1 EN','question_text','Sustainable Development means a kind of development that meets the needs of the present without compromising the ability of ______ generations to meet their own needs'),(540,3,'Text Question Q4.1 ES','question_text','El desarrollo sostenible significa un tipo de desarrollo que satisface las necesidades del presente sin comprometer la capacidad de ______ generaciones para satisfacer sus propias necesidades'),(540,4,'Text Question Q4.1 FR','question_text','Le développement durable désigne un type de développement qui répond aux besoins du présent sans compromettre la capacité des ______ générations à répondre à leurs propres besoins.'),(540,5,'Text Question Q4.1 IT','question_text','Sviluppo sostenibile significa sviluppo che risponde ai bisogni del presente senza compromettere la capacità delle ______ generazioni di soddisfare i propri bisogni '),(541,1,'Text Question Q4.2 BG','question_text','Кое от изброените не е принцип на устойчивото развитие? '),(541,2,'Text Question Q4.2 E