heure. Ici, l\'énergie consommée est de 5 W pendant 20 heures pendant 350 jours. Le calcul à faire est donc : 5 * 20 * 350 = 35000 Wh'),(806,5,'Learning Pill Q1.7 IT','text','Il consumo di energia si misura in Watt-ora, cioè l\'energia consumata da un apparecchio (espressa in watt) durante un\'ora. L\'unità di misura è il Watt-ora o il KiloWatt-ora. In questo caso, l\'energia consumata è di 5 W per 20 ore per 350 giorni. \nIl calcolo da fare è quindi: 5 * 20 * 350 = 35000 Wh.'),(807,1,'Learning Pill Q1.8 BG','text','35kWh означава използване на 35*1000 вата, използвани за 1 час.'),(807,2,'Learning Pill Q1.8 EN','text','35kWh means using 35 * 1000  watts used during 1 hour.'),(807,3,'Learning Pill Q1.8 ES','text','35kWh significa utilizar 35 * 1000 vatios durante 1 hora.'),(807,4,'Learning Pill Q1.8 FR','text','35kWh signifie que 35 * 1000 watts sont uilisés pendant 1 heure.'),(807,5,'Learning Pill Q1.8 IT','text','35kWh significa usare 35 * 1000 watt durante 1 ora.'),(808,1,'Learning Pill Q1.9 BG','text','Изчислено е, че през 2022 г. са били продадени 5,3 милиона гейминг конзоли.'),(808,2,'Learning Pill Q1.9 EN','text','It is estimated that 5,3 million game stations were sold in 2022'),(808,3,'Learning Pill Q1.9 ES','text','Se estima que en 2022 se vendieron 5,3 millones de estaciones de juegos'),(808,4,'Learning Pill Q1.9 FR','text','On estime que 5,3 millions de stations de jeux ont été vendues en 2022.'),(808,5,'Learning Pill Q1.9 IT','text','Si stima che nel 2022 siano stati venduti 5,3 milioni di postazioni di gioco.'),(809,1,'Learning Pill Q1.10 BG','text','35 kWh * 5 000 000 = 175 тераWh. Не е зле, нали? '),(809,2,'Learning Pill Q1.10 EN','text','35 kWh * 5 000 000 = 175 teraWh. Not bad, isn’t it?'),(809,3,'Learning Pill Q1.10 ES','text','35 kWh * 5 000 000 = 175 teraWh. ¡No está nada mal!'),(809,4,'Learning Pill Q1.10 FR','text','35 kWh * 5 000 000 = 175 teraWh. Pas si mal, n\'est-ce pas ?'),(809,5,'Learning Pill Q1.10 IT','text','35 kWh * 5 000 000 = 175 te